### Patient Endpoints (Use token from patient login)

### Book an appointment
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patient/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "doctorId": "DOCTOR_ID",
  "date": "2025-09-20",
  "time": "10:00 AM",
  "reason": "Regular checkup"
}

### View my appointments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patient/appointments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### View my reports
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patient/reports
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Doctor Endpoints (Use token from doctor login)

### View my appointments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/doctor/appointments
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update appointment status
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/doctor/appointments/APPOINTMENT_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

### Create prescription
POST http://localhost:5000/api/doctor/prescriptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "patientId": "PATIENT_ID",
  "appointmentId": "APPOINTMENT_ID",
  "medicines": [
    {
      "name": "Paracetamol",
      "dosage": "500mg",
      "frequency": "Twice daily",
      "duration": "5 days"
    }
  ],
  "diagnosis": "Fever",
  "notes": "Take with food"
}

